  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>A living fire burns within the egg, the haunting pale glow of a lifeform that must provide its own light.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be <span class=\"name name-special\">gelatinous</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">luminescent</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个有生命的、可生育的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>蛋壳内有一团熊熊燃烧的生命之火，散发着不同寻常的苍白光芒，这一定是生命体自己创造的光源。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-special\">胶质</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">荧光</span>的基因潜质。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命、可孵化的蛋，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且即將孵化！</span><br><br>蛋內有一團熊熊燃燒的火焰生命體，其自身散發出的蒼白光芒久久不滅。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下形容的大小及特徵：<span class=\"name name-special\">膠狀</span>且<span class=\"name name-stellar\">會發光</span>。"
  },
